  "text": "Even if reaction time and observational indices of imitation are not measuring the same thing, they could be indexing different component processes of a broader phenomenaautomatic imitation [CITATION_1] . Therefore, it is possible that both measures could be interesting to study in their own right, in order to understand mechanisms underpinning imitation behaviour, while not sharing any direct relationship to each other.",
